      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "贺方"
      ],
      "text": "忙将破胆惊天事，报与金枝玉叶人。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00003",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺方"
      ],
      "text": "大王有请。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00004",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众兵引杨林同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00005",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "日月依龙德，风云挟虎豹。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00006",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺方"
      ],
      "text": "贺方参见。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00007",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "秦琼可曾拿到？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00008",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺方"
      ],
      "text": "秦琼走了。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00009",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "吓，怎么走了？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00010",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺方"
      ],
      "text": "奉大王命令捉拿秦琼，到他营中，说昨晚黄昏时候有一军官手执令箭，说奉大王将令，差秦琼往潼关公干，因此连夜走了。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00011",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "那军官一定是奸细了，查出一同斩首！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00012",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "贺方"
      ],
      "text": "得令。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00013",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "上官仪上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00014",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "上官仪"
      ],
      "text": "智号人中杰，威风阃外司。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00015",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "上官仪"
      ],
      "text": "上官仪告见。大王在上，上官仪交令。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00016",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "收令，命你郊外巡缉，怎么样了？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00017",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "上官仪"
      ],
      "text": "奉大王将令，郊外巡缉，见一被杀妇人，尸旁有男子衣帽，小将下马仔细检验，原来是歌姬紫嫣，特来告知。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00018",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "呼呼咦呀！原来是紫嫣这贱婢！背地里听孤之言，盗吾令箭，报知秦琼知晓，秦琼马上驮带妇人不便，将紫嫣杀死，竟自逃走。可恼啊实可恼！上官仪听令！",
      "text_length": 69
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00019",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
