    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00080",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 80,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "兵甲"
      ],
      "text": "我打、打得他兵似泥来将似齑，𠮾才才得个逍遥云际。呀！早来到，玉关岩、铁索围。关上有人么？什么人？原来是太保，这身披挂要向何往？奉大王将令，要出潼关公干的。可有令箭！有。呈上来。啊，妙啊！凭着这羽箭儿，赛过文移，果然有大王令箭，开关，请！",
      "text_length": 118
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00081",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 81,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "兵甲下。秦琼（白）啊，哈哈……且喜被俺赚出关来也，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00082",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 82,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "刮地风好一似他乡遇故知。啊呀亲娘吓，痛慈亲珠泪垂，𠮾呵痛慈亲珠泪垂。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00083",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 83,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦琼下。杨林、众兵同上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00084",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 84,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "雄关暗袭，窃符虎帐如姬急。偷过函关，商君殛，超海威，拔山力，垂天翼。貔貅勇猛罹锋镝，山川搜索穷南北。军威振，声名赫。",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00085",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 85,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨林、众兵同下。秦琼上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00086",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 86,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "四门子",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "",
      "text_length": 0
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00087",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 87,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "夹白",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00088",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 88,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四门子半空中，隐隐征尘起看，看、看、看连天展羽麾。听、听、听、听喧天鼓角来何地？𠮾呀！这、这的是老大王带马追。马呵！步儿要忙，鞭儿要催，休比那等闲间看花游嬉。兵儿似雄，马儿似龙，呀！忙整顿冲天壮气。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/709011182022-09-02",
      "text_length": 148
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00089",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 89,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨林、众兵同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00090",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 90,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "秦琼哪里走？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00091",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 91,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "大王，俺秦琼并无过犯，为何提兵追赶？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00092",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 92,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "勾引响马，大反山东、火烧仓库，还说无罪，看枪！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00093",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 93,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "老大王，那都是贺方谗言，与俺秦琼何干？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00094",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 94,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "盗孤令箭、杀孤爱姬，私出潼关，还说无罪，看枪！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00095",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 95,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "老大王，你再三逼迫，秦琼无义了。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00096",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 96,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "秦琼、杨林同战，秦琼败下。众兵（同白）秦琼败下。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00097",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 97,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "追",
      "text_length": 1
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00098",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 98,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨林、众兵同下。程咬金上。程咬金（念）髫龄识、髫龄识，念患难同今昔。云天谊、云天谊，念生死同休戚。（白）咱程咬金。奉了徐大哥之令，前来接应秦二哥。一路行来，闻得二哥与杨林这老儿战了一日一夜，追至石龙桥，我此时不去接应，更待何时？（念）合兵敌、势男力，捐躯报效，敢惮荆棘。",
      "text_length": 135
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00099",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 99,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨林、秦琼同杀上，程咬金接战。程咬金（白）呔！杨林哪里走！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00100",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 100,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "杀了半日，杀出一伙毛贼来了。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00101",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 101,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "什么毛贼不毛贼，放马过来。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00102",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 102,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杨林"
      ],
      "text": "饶你们这伙毛贼去吧。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00103",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 103,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "去你的吧！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00104",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 104,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杨林败下。秦琼上。程咬金（白）二哥，兄弟程咬金在此。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00105",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 105,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "原来是兄弟，亏你助力了。哈哈……",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00106",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 106,
      "seq_in_scene": 106,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "程咬金"
      ],
      "text": "秦二哥，做的什么官，还是当强盗的好。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00107",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 107,
      "seq_in_scene": 107,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "秦琼"
      ],
      "text": "咳，罢了是罢了。（尾声）权向山林学避世，论英雄，怎做得束手攒眉。程咬金",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901118_e00108",
      "play_id": "70901118",
      "scene_id": "70901118_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 108,
      "seq_in_scene": 108,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尾声",
      "speakers": [
